abstract: The second-season premiere of "The Walking Dead" was the highest-rated drama episode ever on cable among viewers 18 to 49.
snippet: The second-season premiere of "The Walking Dead" was the highest-rated drama episode ever on cable among viewers 18 to 49.
lead_paragraph: After a recent episode of "The Walking Dead" that vividly revealed the contents of a zombie's stomach, AMC has decided it still has a healthy appetite for that popular series about the survivors of an undead apocalypse.

headline.main: It's a No-Brainer: AMC Orders Third Season of 'The Walking Dead'
